(76, 'Chemical Guys HOL203 Black Car Care Kit, 9 Items', '137', '93', 50, 'product-featured-76.jpg', '<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.255; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); margin-top: 0px; font-size: 17px; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin-bottom: 6px !important;\">Chemical Guys Black Car Kit</h3><h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini a-color-secondary a-text-italic\" style=\"font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.255; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 17px; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(86, 89, 89) !important; margin-bottom: 6px !important; font-style: italic !important;\">About This Kit</h4><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">The Chemical Guys Black Car Kit combines everything needed to maintain the perfect show-winning shine on any black car. Black cars are prized for their distinct luxurious and intimidating look, but keeping them swirl-free is almost a full time job! The key to a swirl and scratch free finish is proper maintenance and protection. The Black Car Kit contains all the premium cleansers, gloss enhancers, wax, applicators, and towels needed to clean, enhance, and protect black cars without scratching the finish. Most swirls and scratches come from washing and drying with poor quality soaps and towels. Chemical Guys Hybrid V7 High Gloss Car Wash Soap lifts and lubricates abrasive dirt and debris with slick foamy suds before they can scratch paintwork. Premium Monster Edgeless Microfiber Towels dry water off the surface with a soft touch that traps any missed dirt for a scratch-free drying experience. The Black Car Kit also comes stocked with Black Light Hybrid Radiant Finish to enhance deep gloss and reflection, and Butter Wet Wax for durable protection with a warm wet shine. Apply your favorite glazes, waxes, and sealants with two premium ultra-soft black Hex-Logic hand pads. Maintain the scratch-free shine between full washes and remove light dirt, dust, or fingerprints with Hybrid V7 Quick Detail Spray. Pick up the Chemical Guys Black Car Kit to clean, enhance, and protect any black car with a scratch-free finish.</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Perfect for black and dark colored paintwork</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Cleans, enhances, and protects any black car</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Helps prevent any swirls or scratches</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Stocked with premium soap, glaze, and wax for black cars</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Premium microfiber towels and soft foam applicators further reduce scratches</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">- Maintain the scratch-free shine with Hybrid V7 Detail Spray</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><br></p><h3 class=\"a-spacing-small\" style=\"font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.255; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 17px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Clean, Enhance and Protect Black Cars</h3><div class=\"apm-floatleft apm-wrap\" style=\"width: 969px; float: left; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"apm-leftimage\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 300px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sota/b11059cc-0ca2-4bc4-b3dc-a46cf3b4302c._SL300__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-mini\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sota/b11059cc-0ca2-4bc4-b3dc-a46cf3b4302c._SL300__.jpg\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 6px !important;\"></div><div class=\"apm-rightthirdcol\" style=\"float: right; width: 230px; padding-left: 30px; margin-left: 30px; border-left: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><div class=\"apm-rightthirdcol-inner\"></div></div><div class=\"apm-centerthirdcol\" style=\"min-width: 359px;\"><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">Over 95% of swirls and scratches come from improper washing and drying tools and techniques. Hybrid V7 High Gloss Car Wash Soap provides slick lubrication and mountains of foamy suds to lift and guide abrasive dirt and debris off from paintwork before it can scratch the finish. Use Hybrid V7 Car Wash Soap in the two bucket wash method or in any foam gun or foam cannon for extra gentle cleaning power. Chemical Guys premium car wash soaps are perfect for any exterior surface on any vehicle. Use Hybrid V7 Car Wash Soap to clean paintwork, wheels, undercarriages, glass, polished metal, plastic, and more. Hybrid V7 is pH-balanced and will not spot or stain even in direct sunlight. The ultra-slick lubricants and gloss enhancers help ensure a scratch free wash and restore that \'just detailed\' look with every wash. Finish off by drying sensitive paintwork with the premium Monster Edgeless Microfiber Towels. The Black Edgeless towels are made with premium 70/30 blend microfiber for an extra-soft touch. Microfiber absorbs water for a spot-free finish, and picks up and traps any dirt missed during the wash for a scratch-free shine. The edgeless towel design further reduces friction on painted surfaces and the chances of installing swirls or scratches. The Black Car Kit contains everything needed to gently clean black cars without causing any swirls or scratches.Black cars are loved for their distinct look and unmatched depth in color. The Black Car Kit comes with Black Light Hybrid Radiant Finish, which is renowned for its gloss and depth enhancing properties. Spread a thin, even coat of Black Light with one of the included Hex-Logic black hand applicator pads over all black paintwork on the vehicle. The Hex-Logic pad uses a super high porosity foam for an extra soft scratchless touch and even product spread on any painted surface. Wait 20 minutes for the product to cure, then buff off any residue with the premium Black Edgeless towels. Take the second Hex-Logic applicator and apply the Butter Wet Wax over all painted, polished metal, glass, and clear optical plastic surfaces on the exterior of the vehicle. Butter Wet Wax enhances black paintwork with a warm wet glow, and protects paintwork, metal, glass, and clear plastic from the elements like pollution, UV sunlight, water, insects, birds, brake dust, and more. Spread a thin, even coat just like the Black Light with the Hex-Logic applicator pad, wait 20 minutes for product to cure, then buff off any excess. When maintained with Hybrid V7 Car Wash Soap and Detail Spray, Butter Wet Wax can protect vehicles for up to 6 months with just one application.The best cure for swirls and scratches is prevention. The only way to actually \'fix\' or remove scratches permanently is to polish them with a machine polisher and compound. Polishing physically removes a thin layer of paint to \'cut\' beneath the scratch to reveal a flat paint surface. A better solution is to prevent scratches from occurring in the first place. Using the Black Car Kit and proper detailing methods drastically reduces the chances of scratching paintwork on any black car. Since washing, drying, and quick detail touchups are the most performed tasks on any car, the Black Car Kit comes with premium car wash soap, microfiber towels, and quick detail spray for maximum lubrication and soft touch when removing dirt from sensitive paintwork. Hybrid V7 Car Wash Soap and Quick Detail Spray lubricate dirt and guide it off paintwork before it can scratch any finish. Black Light and Butter Wet Wax enhance deep black gloss and wet shine while repelling harmful elements like UV sunlight, water, pollution, brake dust, and road grime. The Chemical Guys Black Car Kit is the perfect choice for anyone who wants to keep their black car looking good for years to come.</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: small;\">The Chemical Guys Black Car Kit combines everything needed to maintain the perfect show-winning shine on any black car. Black cars are prized for their distinct luxurious and intimidating look, but keeping them swirl-free is almost a full-time job! The key to a swirl and scratch free finish is proper maintenance and protection. The Black Car Kit contains all the premium cleansers, gloss enhancers, wax, applicators, and towels needed to clean, enhance, and protect black cars without scratching the finish. Over 95 percent of swirls and scratches come from washing and drying with poor quality soaps and towels. Chemical Guys Hybrid V7 High Gloss Car Wash Soap lifts and lubricates abras